{"id":16529,"date":"2019-04-08T16:46:15","date_gmt":"2019-04-08T09:46:15","guid":{"rendered":"\/?p=16529"},"modified":"2020-02-18T11:27:34","modified_gmt":"2020-02-18T04:27:34","slug":"huong-dan-su-dung-mailchimp-tao-squeeze-page","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"\/usecase\/huong-dan-su-dung-mailchimp-tao-squeeze-page","title":{"rendered":"H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng MailChimp \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o Squeeze Page mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"highlight\">Ngo\u00e0i email marketing, trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c <strong>h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Mailchimp<\/strong> t\u1ea1o landing page (mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed) gi\u00fap thu th\u1eadp email ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft <strong><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"MailChimp (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"\/out\/mailchimp\" target=\"_blank\">MailChimp<\/a><\/strong> n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi email marketing mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, nh\u01b0ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 MailChimp c\u0169ng c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t t\u00ednh n\u0103ng kh\u00e1 h\u1eefu \u00edch l\u00e0 t\u1ea1o landing page si\u00eau t\u1ed1c v\u00e0 c\u0169ng mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u01b0u v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1ea1o landing page n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a MailChimp nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n landing page c\u1ee7a MailChimp<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"672\" height=\"568\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Email-List-Mailchimp.png\" alt=\"Email List Mailchimp\" class=\"wp-image-16628\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Email-List-Mailchimp.png 672w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Email-List-Mailchimp-218x184.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Email-List-Mailchimp-300x254.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 672px) 100vw, 672px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ea1o landing page chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, MailChimp th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf ch\u1ec9 cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o 2 lo\u1ea1i landing page ch\u00ednh:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>Squeeze page<\/strong>. L\u00e0 trang d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 thu th\u1eadp email c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ecdc gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng email list. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 page r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n blog c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u00ec v\u1eady t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng MailChimp \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o squeeze page.<\/li><li><strong>Sale page<\/strong>. \u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc, sale page c\u1ee7a MailChimp ch\u1ec9 li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Square. Kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 WordPress. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua t\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u00e0y.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o th\u00eam b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft sau \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n v\u1ec1 Landing Page<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"\/design\/landing-page-la-gi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Landing page l\u00e0 g\u00ec? Blogger c\u00f3 n\u00ean d\u00f9ng landing page? (opens in a new tab)\">Landing page l\u00e0 g\u00ec? Blogger c\u00f3 n\u00ean d\u00f9ng landing page?<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>T\u1ea1i sao b\u1ea1n n\u00ean d\u00f9ng landing page c\u1ee7a MailChimp trong khi b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o page v\u1edbi WordPress<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"980\" height=\"648\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/lead-gen-article-header.png\" alt=\"lead-gen-article-header\" class=\"wp-image-16662\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/lead-gen-article-header.png 980w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/lead-gen-article-header-218x144.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/lead-gen-article-header-300x198.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/lead-gen-article-header-700x463.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/lead-gen-article-header-768x508.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 980px) 100vw, 980px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>T\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u00e0i nguy\u00ean mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed c\u1ee7a MailChimp<\/strong>. \u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t trang th\u00ec b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao nhi\u00eau t\u00e0i nguy\u00ean website, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u trang squeeze page th\u00ec c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1 kh\u00e1 t\u00e0i nguy\u00ean. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan tr\u1ecdng n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c host cloud cao c\u1ea5p v\u1edbi chi ph\u00ed t\u00e0i nguy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t cao.<\/li><li><strong>T\u1ea1o trang Squeeze Page si\u00eau t\u1ed1c<\/strong>. Ch\u1ecdn ngay theme m\u1eabu v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00ec c\u00e1c m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf c\u1ee7a MailChimp \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p. \u0110i\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m l\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn Form, up l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, s\u1eeda v\u0103n b\u1ea3n v\u00e0 l\u01b0u.<\/li><li><strong>S\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang d\u00f9ng MailChimp l\u00e0m Autoresponder ch\u00ednh cho website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/strong>. Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i, form MailChimp v\u00e0 landing page MailChimp \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng v\u1edbi nhau m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u1ed7i t\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00edch n\u00e0o. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y y\u00eau th\u00edch nh\u1ea5t v\u00ec gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ee1 nh\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u khi mu\u1ed1n nh\u00fang form MailChimp v\u00e0o website c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<h2>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng MailChimp \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o Squeeze page t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1<\/strong>: T\u1ea1o landing page m\u1edbi. V\u00e0o <em>Campaigns &gt; Create Campaign &gt; Landing Page<\/em><\/li><li><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 2<\/strong>: \u0110\u1eb7t t\u00ean &gt; Ch\u1ecdn List<\/li><li><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 3<\/strong>: Ch\u1ecdn m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1eb5n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p &gt; Lead Generation<\/li><li><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 4<\/strong>: Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf theo \u00fd th\u00edch c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n &gt; Save &amp; Close<\/li><li><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 5<\/strong>: \u0110i\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft: Page Title, URL, Tracking Code&#8230;<\/li><li><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 6<\/strong>: Publish &gt; Copy link v\u00e0 ch\u00e8n v\u00e0o website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"445\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Tao-campaign-moi-1024x445.png\" alt=\"Tao campaign moi\" class=\"wp-image-16640\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Tao-campaign-moi-1024x445.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Ta