.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/bat-dau-thiet-ke-theo-y-thich-cua-ban-768x329.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/bat-dau-thiet-ke-theo-y-thich-cua-ban.png 1919w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: Tu\u1ef3 ch\u1ec9nh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf theo \u00fd c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"630\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/dien-thong-tin-va-publish-1024x630.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-16646\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/dien-thong-tin-va-publish-1024x630.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/dien-thong-tin-va-publish-218x134.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/dien-thong-tin-va-publish-300x185.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/dien-thong-tin-va-publish-700x431.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/dien-thong-tin-va-publish-768x472.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/dien-thong-tin-va-publish.png 1307w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>B\u01b0\u1edbc 5 v\u00e0 6: \u0110i\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea5m n\u00fat PUBLISH<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"450\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/landing-page-Mailchimp-hoan-tat-1024x450.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-16647\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/landing-page-Mailchimp-hoan-tat-1024x450.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/landing-page-Mailchimp-hoan-tat-218x96.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/landing-page-Mailchimp-hoan-tat-300x132.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/landing-page-Mailchimp-hoan-tat-700x308.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/landing-page-Mailchimp-hoan-tat-768x337.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/landing-page-Mailchimp-hoan-tat.png 1163w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>Copy link v\u00e0 ch\u00e8n v\u00e0o b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e2u b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng l\u01b0u \u00fd khi d\u00f9ng Landing Page MailChimp mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>MailChimp Badge<\/strong>. \u1ede g\u00f3i mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn hai style MailChimp Badge l\u00e0 tr\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111en. B\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p l\u00ean t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ecf MailChimp Badge.<\/li><li><strong>MailChimp URL<\/strong>. MailChimp h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf g\u00f3i mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng URL m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi <em>https:\/\/mailchi.mp\/[Generate-Randomly]\/t\u00ean-page-cua-ban<\/em>. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng Custom domain \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 cho trang m\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o URL c\u1ee7a MailChimp.<\/li><li><strong>Nh\u00fang Javascript<\/strong>. MailChimp kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n nh\u00fang c\u00e1c Javascript n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec MailChimp khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 d\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd m\u00e0 th\u00f4i v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u00fd do an to\u00e0n.<br><\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"244\" height=\"339\" 